<div class="card" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #3498db 100%); color: white; padding: 2.5rem 2rem;">
  <div style="margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">
    <span style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: white;">SPARC</span>
    <span style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-left: 0.75rem; vertical-align: middle;">Systemized Policy and Regulatory Controls</span>
  </div>
  <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: 1.05rem;">
    Centralize, track, and operationalize NIST 800-53 controls — from catalog management and controls implementation to test plan results and OSCAL-ready compliance reporting.
  </p>

  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1rem; margin-top: 2rem;">
    <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius: 8px; padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">
      <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700;"><%= @catalog_count %></div>
      <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); margin-top: 0.25rem;">Control Catalogs</div>
    </div>
    <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius: 8px; padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">
      <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700;"><%= @family_count %></div>
      <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); margin-top: 0.25rem;">Control Families</div>
    </div>
    <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius: 8px; padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">
      <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700;"><%= @control_count %></div>
      <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); margin-top: 0.25rem;">Catalog Controls</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1rem; margin-top: 0.75rem;">
    <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius: 8px; padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">
      <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700;"><%= @cdef_count %></div>
      <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); margin-top: 0.25rem;">Component Definitions</div>
    </div>
    <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius: 8px; padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">
      <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700;"><%= @ssp_count %></div>
      <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); margin-top: 0.25rem;">Controls Implementation</div>
    </div>
    <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius: 8px; padding: 1rem; text-align: center;">
      <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700;"><%= @tpr_count %></div>
      <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); margin-top: 0.25rem;">Test Plan Results</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">

  <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 0; text-align: center; border: 2px solid #3498db;">
    <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">&#128218;</div>
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Control Catalogs</h3>
    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; min-height: 2.5rem;">
      Browse NIST SP 800-53 Rev 4 and Rev 5 control families and base controls. Add custom catalogs or entries.
    </p>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
      <%= link_to "View Catalogs", control_catalogs_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
      <%= link_to "New Catalog", new_control_catalog_path, class: "btn btn-success" %>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.5rem; background: var(--surface-alt); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--link-accent);">
      NIST SP 800-53 Rev 4 &amp; Rev 5 pre-loaded
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 0; text-align: center;">
    <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">&#128737;</div>
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Component Definitions</h3>
    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; min-height: 2.5rem;">
      Import DISA STIGs, SCAP, and CIS benchmarks. Export OSCAL-compliant Component Definitions.
    </p>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
      <%= link_to "View CDEFs", cdef_documents_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
      <%= link_to "Upload New", new_cdef_document_path, class: "btn btn-success" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 0; text-align: center;">
    <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">&#128196;</div>
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Controls Implementation</h3>
    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; min-height: 2.5rem;">
      Upload and manage controls implementation workbooks. Edit editable fields, track status, and export to JSON.
    </p>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
      <%= link_to "View Documents", ssp_documents_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
      <%= link_to "Upload New", new_ssp_document_path, class: "btn btn-success" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 0; text-align: center;">
    <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">&#128203;</div>
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Test Plan Results</h3>
    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; min-height: 2.5rem;">
      Upload multi-tab test plan workbooks. View results by section, asset, and environment with heat maps by control family.
    </p>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
      <%= link_to "View Documents", tpr_documents_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
      <%= link_to "Upload New", new_tpr_document_path, class: "btn btn-success" %>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<div class="card">
  <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">Features</h3>
  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.5rem 2rem;">
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; padding: 0.4rem 0;">
      <span style="color: #27ae60; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;">&#10003;</span>
      <span>Convert Excel workbooks (Controls Implementation &amp; Test Plan Results) to JSON</span>
    </div>
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; padding: 0.4rem 0;">
      <span style="color: #27ae60; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;">&#10003;</span>
      <span>NIST SP 800-53 Rev 4 &amp; Rev 5 control catalogs pre-loaded</span>
    </div>
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; padding: 0.4rem 0;">
      <span style="color: #27ae60; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;">&#10003;</span>
      <span>Edit control fields with read-only enforcement</span>
    </div>
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; padding: 0.4rem 0;">
      <span style="color: #27ae60; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;">&#10003;</span>
      <span>Interactive heat maps by NIST control family</span>
    </div>
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; padding: 0.4rem 0;">
      <span style="color: #27ae60; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;">&#10003;</span>
      <span>Export documents to JSON</span>
    </div>
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; padding: 0.4rem 0;">
      <span style="color: #27ae60; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;">&#10003;</span>
      <span>Click-to-filter controls by family and status</span>
    </div>
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; padding: 0.4rem 0;">
      <span style="color: #27ae60; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;">&#10003;</span>
      <span>Bulk update capabilities via API</span>
    </div>
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; padding: 0.4rem 0;">
      <span style="color: #27ae60; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;">&#10003;</span>
      <span>Manage custom catalogs, families, and controls</span>
    </div>
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; padding: 0.4rem 0;">
      <span style="color: #27ae60; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;">&#10003;</span>
      <span>Import component definitions from XCCDF XML (DISA STIGs, SCAP, CIS) and JSON (InSpec, STIG Viewer)</span>
    </div>
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.6rem; padding: 0.4rem 0;">
      <span style="color: #27ae60; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;">&#10003;</span>
      <span>Export OSCAL-compliant Component Definitions (NIST OSCAL v1.1.2)</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
